metadata.name: Nothing That You Do
metadata.description:
A 1 of 1 unique fine art high res photograph NFT.

This abandoned derelict farm house, shot on a cold February afternoon as the sun started to set is located in rural southern Alberta Canada. It is known as the Laing house and sits below a prairie rise near the small town of Carbon. 


License Information: Primary NFT holder is free to used purchased NFTs in private displays, in groups, in virtual galleries, documentaries and essays by the holder with credit to the creator. Purchase provides no rights to create commercial merchandise, commercial distribution or derivative works.
